data.description: 20 acres with a 3/2 bath log cabin plus a detached mother-in-law or guest house with a living room and kitchen, 1 bedroom and a bathroom.  This property has plenty of space for horses or cows. It also has 2 ponds, one is stocked, a large chicken coop, 4 stall barn, 10 acres of nice hardwood pines towards the back of the property, RV hookup as well as additional mobile home pad and hookups. The main house has a large covered porch around the exterior and an open interior space. The living, dining and kitchen all look into each other. The kitchen was remodeled as has concrete countertops, an island, newer cabinets, s/s appliances and lots of counter space. The living room has a charming wood fireplace. The HVAC is new and the roof was replaced in the spring of 2017. This home has a lot of charm, character and is a must see! Call to schedule an appointment today
